      "effect": "Target 1 \"The Phantom Knights\" or \"Xyz Dragon\" monster in your GY or banishment; Special Summon it (but negate its effects), then Special Summon from your Extra Deck, 1 \"The Phantom Knights\" or \"Xyz Dragon\" Xyz Monster that is 1 Rank higher than a DARK Xyz Monster you control, by using that monster as material (this is treated as an Xyz Summon, transfer its materials). You can only activate 1 \"The Phantom Knights' Rank-Up-Magic Requiem\" per turn.",
